{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/make/oled-button-cy7031","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>I proudly present <a href=\"https://github.com/mikolasan/oledbutton\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">OledButton class and tools</a> that is created to manage <a href=\"http://www.cyo.com.tw/evaluation_kit.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">evaluation kit <strong>CY-7031</strong></a> for OLED button <strong>CY-3031</strong> through serial port (RS485).</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.cyo.com.tw/images/product/CY-7031.jpg\" alt=\"CY-7031\"> <img src=\"http://www.cyo.com.tw/images/product/CY-2031.jpg\" alt=\"CY-3031\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"install\" style=\"position:relative;\">Install<a href=\"#install\" aria-label=\"install permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Written on Python 3.5. I have no idea how it works on other previous versions. Do not try Python 2 because of new types such as <code class=\"language-text\">bytes</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">bytearray</code>.</p>\n<p>You need:</p>\n<p>Inevitable <a href=\"http://pyserial.readthedocs.org/en/latest/pyserial_api.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>PySerial</strong></a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">pip install pyserial</code></pre></div>\n<p>Advisable <a href=\"https://pillow.readthedocs.org/en/3.1.x/handbook/tutorial.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Pillow</strong> (PIL fork)</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">pip install Pillow</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>numpy</strong> to <a href=\"https://toster.ru/q/298153\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">convert</a> any image to bmp565 format</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">pip install numpy</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"run\" style=\"position:relative;\">Run<a href=\"#run\" aria-label=\"run permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Look inside <code class=\"language-text\">main.py</code>, write your own workflow and run</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">python main.py</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.7717391304347827;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cedb497e62dc40cbe8b4bf6422af8937/768c6/ole